Privacy Policy for PDFMergomatic

PDFMergomatic respects your privacy. This application does not collect, store, or share any personal user data.

The app works entirely on your device to merge PDF files selected by the user. No files are uploaded to any server.

Advertising:
This app uses Google AdMob to display ads. AdMob may collect anonymous usage data such as device information, advertising ID, and interactions with ads to improve ad performance. This data is handled according to Google’s Privacy Policy.

File Access:
The app only accesses PDF files that the user explicitly selects. Files are processed locally on the device and are not transmitted externally.

Children’s Privacy:
This app is not specifically designed for children under the age of 13 and does not knowingly collect personal information from children.

Changes:
This privacy policy may be updated if necessary. Any changes will be reflected on this page.

Contact:
If you have questions about this privacy policy, you can contact us at:
support@pdfmergomatic.com
